<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Offline - AURIX</title>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#6366f1">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #0f0f1a;
            color: #f8fafc;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .offline-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #ec4899);
            border-radius: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            font-size: 48px;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.8; }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #ec4899);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            max-width: 400px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #4f46e5);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
        }

        .cached-pages {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .cached-pages h3 {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .cached-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #f8fafc;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cached-link:hover {
            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
        }

        .cached-link i {
            color: #6366f1;
        }

        .status-indicator {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .status-indicator::before {
            content: '';
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: blink 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.3; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .offline-icon {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
                font-size: 32px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="offline-icon">
        <span>📡</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="status-indicator">
        You're offline
    </div>
    
    <h1>No Internet Connection</h1>
    <p>It looks like you've lost your internet connection. Don't worry - you can still browse cached pages or try reconnecting.</p>
    
    <button class="btn" onclick="window.location.reload()">
        <span>🔄</span>
        Try Again
    </button>

    <div class="cached-pages">
        <h3>Available Offline</h3>
        <a href="/" class="cached-link">
            <span>🏠</span>
            <span>Homepage</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/#portfolio" class="cached-link">
            <span>💼</span>
            <span>Portfolio</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="cached-link">
            <span>📧</span>
            <span>Contact</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Check connection status periodically
        setInterval(() => {
            if (navigator.onLine) {
                window.location.reload();
            }
        }, 5000);

        // Listen for online event
        window.addEventListener('online', () => {
            window.location.reload();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
